quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  63,4,"Ne nobalola, emibili chiabu chikhuchamisia, ne nibaboola orechelesia amakhuwa kabu, opara mbu ni emisala chiyeshibwe, baparanga mbu buli oluyoka lwosi lwosi lupwa lulikhubo. Abo nibo Abasuku ba meso ninabo, Nyasaye yabatsuba, bakoranga barie abwatoto"
  63,5,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu itse Omurumwa abasabile eshileshelo, bayuyia emirwe chiabu, ne obalola nibashukhana nibafurire"
  63,6,"Ninashilala khubo, nobasabila eshileshelo nohomba nolekha, Nyasaye shiyakhabaleshela tawe, toto Nyasaye shalunjisinjia abonooni tawe"
  63,7,"Nibo baboolonga mbu mulakhoonya balia abali halala nomurumwa tawe, ukhula bamwilushe, ne Nyasaye ni Mwene emikabo chio mwikulu nende mushialo, halali abeshikhabili shibamanyile tawe"
  63,8,"Baboolanga mbu nikhukalukha Madina abamaani balaloonda abateshele, Ne amani ni ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe nende Abasuubili, halali Abeshikhabili shibamanyile tawe"
  63,9,"Enywe Abasuubili, omwandu nende Abana benyu bilachila mwebilila okhumurumbula Nyasaye tawe, ne yesi yesi ukhola ario, aba ali mubatiba"
  63,10,"Ne murusie eshihanwa mumiandu chia khwabahelesia, lifwa nilishili okhulila mulala wenyu, mana aboole mbu : “Abaanyiee Nyasaye wanje umetakhwo tsinyanga atiti ndakharusiye eshihanwa, mana ndaba mubandu abalayi"
  63,11,"Ne Nyasaye shanyala okhumeta Omundu ebise lifwa lilie niliakhoola tawe, ne Nyasaye nomumanyi muno khukamukholanga"
  64,1,"Bitsoominjia Nyasaye biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, obwami nobuubwe nende oluyali, naye ni Omunyali wa buli eshindu"
  64,2,"Ye niye Owabaloonga ne mwinywe balimwo Abakhayi nende Abasuubili, ne Nyasaye alolanga muno kamukholanga"
  64,3,"Yalonga likuli nende eshialo khubwatoto mana nabahelesia obukoondo, obulayi, ne ewuwe niwo wamulikalukha"
  64,4,"Yamanya ebili mwikulu nende mushialo ne yamanya kamukholanga mubwifisi nende mubwang’angu, Ne Nyasaye nomumanyi muno khukali mumioyo"
  64,5,"Shimwawulilakhwo amacheni kabakhayi abaali imbeli wenyu, bapila omurungo kwa mabii kabu, mana nibaba nende eshinyasio eshilulu"
  64,6,"Endio nilwokhubeela mbu babetselanga Abarumwa babu nende obwatoto mana nibamiena mbu: “Omundusa akhuruke !” mana nibakhaya nibafura, Mana Nyasaye nalabateba tawe, ne Nyasaye nomuyinda witsomibungwa muno"
  64,7,"Abakhayi bapara mbu shibalilamusibwa tawe. Boola mbu : “ toto, nditsuba khu Nyasaye mbu mulilamusibwa mana muliboolelwa kamwakhola, ne ako khu Nyasaye ni amangu"
  64,8,"Kho suubile khu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, nende obulafu bwa khweshia, ne Nyasaye nomumanyi po khukamukholanga"
  64,9,"Inyanga lwa alibakhung’asia khu inyanga yomukhung’aano, eyo niyo inyanga yokhukhobana ne ulia usuubila khu Nyasaye mana akhole amalayi, alaleshelwa tsimbi tsitsie, ne alimwinjisia mwikulu mumikunda chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  64,10,"Ne balia bakhaya nibayingana khubimanyisio biefu, obo nibo Abandu bomumulilo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, ne ni amakalushilo amabii muno"
  64,11,"Ne amasila kosikosi shiketsanga tawe halali khubunyali bwa Nyasaye, ne usuubila khu Nyasaye alunjisia omwoyo kukwe, ne Nyasaye ni amumanyi muno wabuli eshindu"
  64,12,"Ne muloonde amakhuwa ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa , ne nimuloba Omurumwa wefu ni okhusia butswa oburume bubwe habulafu"
  64,13,"Naye ni Nyasaye abulaho owundi owulali ye tawe, ne Abasuubili basiche butswa Nyasaye"
  64,14,"Enywe Abasuubila, toto Mubakhasi benyu nende Abana benyu balimwo abasuku benyu, kho mube meso ninabo, ne nimubeela nemwakhaya okhura mumakani, ne mwaleshela toto bwene Nyasaye ni Omulesheli Owobukoosia muno"
  64,15,"Toto emiandu chienyu nabaana benyu namatemo, ne Nyasaye ali nende omurungo omukhongo"
  64,16,"Ne murie Nyasaye shinga munyalilwa, ne muwulile, mana muloonde ne murusie eshihanwa, nobulayi khumioyo chienyu ne ulia ulekha obwimani bwo mwoyo kukwe, abo nibo babura"
  64,17,"Nimwiwosia Nyasaye likofi lilayi, alabametelakhwo ne alabaleshela ebionono, ne Nyasaye ni Omunji wokhupa orio Omwihotselefu"
  64,18,"Yamanya akefisile nende akali habulafu, Owamaani Owamachesi muno"